data.description: Welcome to your beautifully remodeled 5-bed, 3-bath, 2,800 sq. ft home in Rivilla Park (Mead School District!) This move-in-ready gem features vinyl windows, new kitchen cabinets, and updated bathrooms and flooring. Enjoy the spacious, park-like backyard with plenty of space for entertaining, gathering around the fire pit, and spotting local wildlife. Just minutes from restaurants & coffee shops, this home also offers RV parking and an extra-large garage with shop space. Enjoy private neighborhood access to the Little Spokane River, perfect for kayaking, fishing and swimming. Come discover this coveted neighborhood, where only four homes have sold in the last 3 years. Don't miss the opportunity to make this one yours!
